      "text": "Props:\n  value: string         (← input)\n  onChange(s): void    (← setInput)\n  onSend(s): void       (← addMessage)\n  model: string\n  onModelChange(s): void\n\nRenders:\n  <input> text field\n    Enter key → onSend(value)\n  <select> model picker\n    llama-3.1-8b-instant\n    llama-3.3-70b-versatile\n    openai/gpt-oss-120b\n  <button> send icon  (disabled if empty)",
